chapter.para:
The left panel contains the list of flows that composes the selected line in the previous tab, while the right panel exhibits information of the currently selected flow, divided in two parts:
On the top basic information such as flow title, last modification date and last execution date can be quickly consulted;
On the bottom there is a summary of the flow (see below), but this view can be switched to Snapshots view or Output view, according to the context. Further information is available on and .

