      or even an log file in case an error occurs.

note.para:
Useful keybinds are available here: Ctrl+R runs the selected snapshots
				one after another; Ctrl+Shift+R runs the
				selected snapshots parallely (keybind activated just if multiple snapshots are selected);
				Delete delete the selected snapshots;

